OL,3,CFraudsters steal #629m from UK victims
OL,4,Cas online scams surge
OL,6,FFraudsters stole more than #629
OL,7,Fmillion from UK consumers in the first
OL,8,Fsix months of 2025, a 3% increase on
OL,9,Flast year, according to new figures
OL,10,Ffrom UK Finance.
OL,12,FThe trade body's half-year fraud
OL,13,Freport, released on Friday, reveals
OL,14,Fthat over 2 million confirmed fraud
OL,15,Fcases were recorded between January
OL,16,Fand June - an increase of 17% compared
OL,17,Fto the same period in 2024.
