OL,3,CFraudsters steal #629m from UK victims
OL,4,Cas online scams surge
OL,6,FDespite the increase in criminal
OL,7,Factivity, banks prevented a record
OL,8,F#870 million of unauthorised fraud
OL,9,Fthrough advanced security systems, the
OL,10,Fequivalent of stopping 70 pence in
OL,11,Fevery #1 attempted.
OL,13,FUK Finance warns that most scams now
OL,14,Fstart outside the banking system, with
OL,15,Ftwo-thirds (66%) of authorised push
OL,16,Fpayment (APP) fraud beginning online,
OL,17,Foften through social-media platforms,
OL,18,Ffake adverts or digital marketplaces.
OL,20,FA further 17% started via
OL,21,Ftelecommunications networks.
