OL,4,Cas online scams surge
OL,6,FBen Donaldson, managing director of
OL,7,Feconomic crime at UK Finance, said
OL,8,Fcriminals are "continuing to adapt
OL,9,Fways to steal victims' money and
OL,10,Ffunnel significant sums of money to
OL,11,Fcriminal enterprises".
OL,13,F"Despite ongoing investment by the
OL,14,Findustry, the majority of fraud
OL,15,Foriginates online and over the phone,
OL,16,Fwhere manipulation begins long before
OL,17,Fany payment is made," he said.
