OL,6,F"The scale of the threat is not
OL,7,Fcommensurate with the current level of
OL,8,Fgovernment investment or the
OL,9,Finsufficient action by other sectors."
OL,11,FLosses to authorised push payment
OL,12,Ffraud reached #257.5 million in the
OL,13,Ffirst half of 2025, up 12% year-on-
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FThe sharpest increase came from
OL,17,Finvestment scams, which surged 55% to
OL,18,F#97.7 million, as criminals convinced
OL,19,Fvictims to transfer money into fake
OL,20,Ffunds or bogus investment schemes.
