OL,6,FBanks reimbursed #159.2 million to APP
OL,7,Ffraud victims during the period, equal
OL,8,Fto 62% of total losses.
OL,10,FUK Finance says the financial sector
OL,11,Fcannot tackle the escalating fraud
OL,12,Fcrisis alone.
OL,14,FIt is urging the government's upcoming
OL,15,Ffraud strategy to make prevention a
OL,16,Fnational priority and to hold social-
OL,17,Fmedia and telecoms companies
OL,18,Faccountable for scams originating on
OL,19,Ftheir platforms.
