OL,6,FIf you believe you've been a victim of
OL,7,Ffraud or suspect suspicious activity
OL,8,Fon your account, take action
OL,9,Fimmediately.
OL,11,F1. Contact your bank right away - use
OL,12,Fthe number on the back of your card or
OL,13,Fthe bank's official website.
OL,15,F2. Report the fraud to Action Fraud -
OL,16,Fthe UK's national reporting centre for
OL,17,Fcyber and financial crime: https:/
OL,18,F/www.actionfraud.police.uk
